g 
Places a copy of the current message on your clipboard.

The clipboard is kind of a "holding area" for posts or messages
that you might want to insert into a post or a mail at some later time.
 
To access the clipboard menu, press w<r*w>g from a short prompt.
 
rNotew:  gThere is rnog option in the current WinCLients for inserting the clipboard
       into a post. This is because you can cut and paste with the mouse
       to the Windows clipboard instead.
